ild())\n                                .build())\n                        .build())\n                .build();\n        private static final ResultSetMetadata EMPTY_METADATA = ResultSetMetadata.newBuilder()\n                .setRowType(StructType.newBuilder().build())\n                .build();\n        private static final ResultSetStats QUERY_PLAN_STATS = ResultSetStats.newBuilder()\n                .setQueryPlan(QueryPlan.newBuilder()\n                        .addPlanNodes(PlanNode.newBuilder()\n                                .setIndex(0)\n                                .setDisplayName(\"Distributed Union\")\n                                .build())\n                        .build())\n                .build();\n\n        private final AtomicReference<String> planSql = new AtomicReference<>();\n\n        @Override\n        public void createSession(\n                CreateSessionRequest request, StreamObserver<Session> responseObserver) {\n            responseObserver.onNext(Session.newBuilder()\n                    .setName(request.getDatabase() + \"/sessions/test-session\")\n                    .setMultiplexed(request.getSession().getMultiplexed())\n                    .build());\n            responseObserver.onCompleted();\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public void executeStreamingSql(\n                ExecuteSqlRequest request, StreamObserver<PartialResultSet> responseObserver) {\n            if (request.getQueryMode() == ExecuteSqlRequest.QueryMode.PLAN) {\n                planSql.set(request.getSql());\n                responseObserver.onNext(PartialResultSet.newBuilder()\n                        .setMetadata(EMPTY_METADATA)\n                        .setStats(QUERY_PLAN_STATS)\n                        .build());\n            } else {\n                responseObserver.onNext(PartialResultSet.newBuilder()\n                        .setMetadata(DIALECT_METADATA)\n                        .addValues(Value.newBuilder().setStringValue(DIALECT).build())